  "remarks": "\nDeputy Director of the Munitions Industry Department (MID). In charge of the development of programmes concerning conventional arms and missiles, including ballistic missiles. One of the main persons responsible for the industrial development programmes for nuclear arms. As such, responsible for the DPRK’s nuclear arms-related, ballistic missile-related, or other weapons of mass destruction-related programmes.Witnessed the launch of the Hwasong-15 intercontinental ballistic missile on 28 November 2017.",
